description:
Vicki, the only female member of http://anidb.net/ch50020 [Core-Tech], is feisty and impetuous. Although she is well-educated and culturally aware, she is definitely not a snob.
Vicki has a clever, acerbic wit about her. A born and raised fighter, she applies her strong sense of right and wrong to actionably exercise her intolerance for cheaters, liars and thieves.
name: Vicki
